OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a mostly dry start, the
OL,6,Fday will see bight spells interspersed
OL,7,Fwith blustery showers. These mainly in
OL,8,Fthe west. Strong southerly winds may
OL,9,Freach gale force at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe showers will clear from
OL,12,Fthe evening to leave the night dry
OL,13,Fwith increasing clear periods. This
OL,14,Ftogether with the wind falling light
OL,15,Fwill bring a patchy inland frost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,18,Fwith bright spells. Cloud and
OL,19,Fscattered showers spread northeast
OL,20,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
