OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain spread northeast Wednesday,
OL,8,Fclearing in the east Wednesday night.
OL,9,FThe rain turns showery in the west
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
